
'''''Nakom''''' ni filime yikinamico yakozwe mu mwaka wa 2016 iyobowe na Kelly Daniela Norris na TW Pittman <ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/02/movies/nakom-review.html</ref>.  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 66 rya Berlin mu gice cya Panorama  kandi yatumiriwe kuzerekanwa bwa mbere muri [[Amerika]] y'Amajyaruguru mu iserukiramuco rya new diroctorss i New York<ref>https://www.filmmovement.com/product/nakom</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
